AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 2168 House Bill No. 2089*
by deleting subsection (c) in Section 1 and substituting:
(c) The instruction required in subsection (b) must be taught on Victims of
Communism Day. If Victims of Communism Day falls on a weekend or any day for
which students enrolled in a world history and geography course will not receive
instruction for the course, then the instruction required in subsection (b) must be taught
on the next school day for which such students will receive instruction in the course.
